{"tid":446798,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(小心!!!) 貴重物品勿寄艙行李","createTime":"2017-10-24T15:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T15:42:30.000Z","uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78c42644421ac43e917cff0fccd0e0b3ddba36ff","tid":446798,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:32:33.000Z","msg":"不少人都認為，一般寄艙行李只是放些個人衣物，即使沒有上鎖也不會有人動歪念，但這樣鬆懈隨時會招來小偷！近日港人熱門旅遊地之一的泰國布吉，一名機場行李搬運工人竟公然翻開多名乘客的寄艙行李，即使有人目擊仍照偷無誤。小偷如此猖狂，大家以後一定要鎖好行李，以及貴重物品跟身。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>明目張膽！ 寄艙行李隨手打開</strong><br />\n<br />\n日前社交網站瘋傳一段泰國布吉機場人員，整理寄艙行李時偷竊的影片。影片全長2分40秒，從片段所見，該名身穿工作服、反戴鴨舌帽的年輕行李搬運工人打開沒有上鎖的乘客行李箱，並翻看裡面的行李<br />\n<br />\n<strong>貪得無厭 翻完一個又一個</strong><br />\n<br />\n小偷超級猖狂，把手一再探入行李箱內亂摸，檢查有沒有值錢的東西。他不光對一個行李箱「下手」，翻完一個後，又再翻別人的行李。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>暗格小袋通通打開</strong><br />\n<br />\n小偷翻行李的工夫，可不只是「表面」的。他左翻右翻，壓在衣物下的小袋子也掏出來細看<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/steal_1_193894782459e5ce6cb0119.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsteal_1_193894782459e5ce6cb0119.png&h=2945c551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/steal_3_57698919859e5d0ebd31c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fsteal_3_57698919859e5d0ebd31c8.png&h=8ecfe236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警方到機場緝捕小偷</strong><br />\n<br />\n根據泰國傳媒報道，布吉警方隨即到機場調查，並拘捕涉事行李搬運工人，及後尋回一個藍芽喇叭，並經由機場將失物交還給乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>小偷落網及交還贓物</strong><br />\n<br />\n警方向疑犯展示錄到他犯案的閉路電視影片後，他承認偷竊罪行，並向機場有關部門交還所偷的藍芽喇叭，好讓機場人員將贓物交還物主。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>小偷為外判員工 捷星即時調查事件</strong><br />\n<br />\n據泰國警方透露，小偷年齡27歲，名字是Abdullah Hayee Mayeh，現被控搶劫罪（robbery），交由Saku警局跟進，暫時未知會有甚麼處分。據悉，小偷是行李輸送服務公司BAGS的員工。BAGS現為大約90條泰國航線提供行李搬運服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/22450083_10210578011674666_751768484858221533_n_23840791659e5cb6bc4e96-703x807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F22450083_10210578011674666_751768484858221533_n_23840791659e5cb6bc4e96-703x807.jpg&h=b71e43e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink::<a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/thailand/%E5%AF%84%E8%89%99%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E-%E5%B8%83%E5%90%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E/7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Fthailand%2F%25E5%25AF%2584%25E8%2589%2599%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%258E-%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2590%2589%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2581%25B7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%258E%2F7%2F&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M40jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=00562e94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/thailand/%E5%AF%84%E8%89%99%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E-%E5%B8%83%E5%90%89%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%B7%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%8E/7/</a>"},{"pid":"ece3fd34ddb0ea1e780ddb3be599ba335f7efd9d","tid":446798,"uid":145117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"好偷唔偷 淨係偷個藍芽喇叭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ebf74da9fcca4e10b51a7d540d9dfd584907f0","tid":446798,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd481f01ec0aac81ba13f4a68169f26d350e7d95","tid":446798,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"其實咁熟手 應該好多人都瀨過野?"},{"pid":"a48256dcba597c82a18d564e7e419ea857c451c5","tid":446798,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:37:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72bab658273a0de3d41825ffc1eb2bae6eab7ef5","tid":446798,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot